<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Harts Remodeling & Renovation</title>

<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f4f4f4;
    color: #333;
  }

  header {
    background: #111;
    color: white;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  header h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 32px;
  }

  header p {
    margin: 5px 0 0;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .card {
    background: white;
    padding: 20px;
    margin: 15px 0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  h2 {
    color: #111;
  }

  .services ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .services li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .contact {
    background: #111;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 25px;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 10px 15px;
    background: #e63946;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 15px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #777;
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Harts Remodeling & Renovation</h1>
  <p>Serving Since 2012 | Ruston, Louisiana</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="card">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
      Harts Remodeling & Renovation delivers high-quality home improvement services with over a decade of experience.
      We specialize in residential remodeling, repairs, and upgrades done right the first time.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card services">
    <h2>Our Services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Kitchen Remodeling</li>
      <li>Bathroom Renovation</li>
      <li>Flooring Installation</li>
      <li>Painting</li>
      <li>Drywall Repair & Installation</li>
      <li>Electrical Work</li>
      <li>Tile Work</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>License</h2>
    <p>Licensed Contractor #: <strong>#R-49173</strong></p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
    <p>
      ✔ Reliable & Experienced<br>
      ✔ Quality Craftsmanship<br>
      ✔ Affordable Pricing<br>
      ✔ Honest Work Done Right
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

<div class="contact">
  <h2>Contact Us Today</h2>
  <p>📞 225-317-8437</p>
  <p>📍 Ruston, Louisiana</p>
  <a class="btn" href="tel:2253178437">Call Now</a>
</div>

<footer>
  © 2026 Harts Remodeling & Renovation. All rights reserved.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
